  "body": "Estimated end-of-life date, accurate to within three months: 05-2027\r\nSee [the support level definitions](https://docs.datadoghq.com/tracing/trace_collection/compatibility/python/#releases) for more information.\r\n\r\n### Bug Fixes\r\n\r\n- LLM Observability: Fixes an issue where the `@llm` decorator raised a `LLMObsAnnotateSpanError` exception when a decorated function returned a value that could not be parsed as LLM messages (e.g. a plain string, integer, or non-messages dict). The decorator now logs a debug message instead and continues. Manual annotations via `LLMObs.annotate()` still take precedence."
